snippet.title: Mayday: Conflict Earth cutscenes
snippet.description:
All video cutscenes from the 2000 game Mayday: Conflict Earth by JoWooD / Boris Games.

Original videos are 128x96 and take up most of the game CD. In the game they are upscaled to 640x480 without any interpolation (you can literally count pixels).

Unused German video included at 51:41.
